cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.SY, cs.DC 

This paper is about optimizing the structure of neural network models in federated learning using a multi-objective evolutionary algorithm. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also discusses communication costs, which could fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control) or cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing).
